Icons placeholder directory.

Required icon files (generate with `pnpm tauri icon <source-image>`):
  - 32x32.png       (small app icon)
  - 128x128.png     (medium app icon)
  - icon.icns        (macOS app icon bundle)
  - tray-icon.png   (macOS menu bar tray icon, recommended 22x22 @2x)

Use a template-style monochrome icon for tray-icon.png so macOS
renders it correctly in both light and dark menu bars.
